e-year period following the grant date. Payout is based", "bbox": [112.5, 597.2, 1158.1, 617.0]}, {"text": "upon Occidental's absolute total shareholder return and performance relative to its peers. TSRIs have payouts that range", "bbox": [75.0, 620.9, 1158.0, 640.7]}, {"text": "from 0 to 200 percent of the target award and settle in stock once certified. Dividend equivalents for TSRIs are accumulated", "bbox": [75.0, 644.7, 1158.1, 664.5]}, {"text": "and paid upon certification of the award. The fair value of TSRIs settled in shares during the years ended December 31, 2018,", "bbox": [75.0, 668.4, 1158.1, 688.2]}, {"text": "2017 and 2016 was $12 million, $5 million, and $8 million, respectively.", "bbox": [75.0, 692.2, 700.8, 712.0]}, {"text": "The fair values of TSRIs are initially determined on the grant date using a Monte Carlo simulation model based on", "bbox": [112.5, 716.0, 1158.1, 735.8]}, {"text": "Occidental's assumptions, noted in the following table, and the volatility from corresponding peer group companies. The", "bbox": [75.0, 739.7, 1158.0, 759.5]}, {"text": "expected life is based on the vesting period (Term). The risk-free interest rate is the implied yield available on zero coupon", "bbox": [75.0, 763.5, 1158.0, 783.3]}, {"text": "T-notes (U.S. Treasury Strip) at the time of grant with a remaining term equal to the Term. The dividend yield is the expected", "bbox": [75.0, 787.2, 1158.1, 807.0]}, {"text": "annual dividend yield over the Term, expressed as a percentage of the stock price on the grant date. Estimates of fair value", "bbox": [75.0, 811.0, 1158.0, 830.8]}, {"text": "may not accurately predict the value ultimately realized by the employees who receive the awards, and the ultimate value", "bbox": [75.0, 834.7, 1158.0, 854.5]}, {"text": "may not be indicative of the reasonableness of the original estimates of fair value made by Occidental.", "bbox": [75.0, 858.5, 975.3, 878.3]}, {"text": "The grant-date assumptions used in the Monte Carlo simulation models for the estimated payout level of TSRIs were as", "bbox": [112.5, 882.3, 1158.1, 902.1]}, {"text": "follows:", "bbox": [75.0, 906.0, 141.0, 925.8]}, {"text": "TSRIs", "bbox": [949.7, 947.5, 994.8, 967.3]}, {"text": "Year Granted", "bbox": [81.3, 974.6, 177.3, 994.4]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [831.2, 974.6, 867.3, 994.4]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [954.1, 974.6, 990.2, 994.4]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [1077.1, 974.6, 1113.2, 994.4]}, {"text": "Assumptions used:", "bbox": [81.3, 1001.7, 231.9, 1021.5]}, {"text": "Risk-free interest rate", "bbox": [106.3, 1028.8, 261.5, 1048.6]}, {"text": "2.3%", "bbox": [869.5, 1028.8, 906.6, 1048.6]}, {"text": "1.5%", "bbox": [992.5, 1028.8, 1029.5, 1048.6]}, {"text": "0.8%", "bbox": [1115.4, 1028.8, 1152.5, 1048.6]}, {"text": "Dividend yield", "bbox": [106.3, 1055.9, 207.3, 1075.7]}, {"text": "4.4%", "bbox": [869.5, 1055.9, 906.5, 1075.7]}, {"text": "4.5%", "bbox": [992.4, 1055.9, 1029.5, 1075.7]}, {"text": "3.9%", "bbox": [1115.4, 1055.9, 1152.5, 1075.7]}, {"text": "Volatility factor", "bbox": [106.2, 1082.9, 211.4, 1102.7]}, {"text": "24%", "bbox": [874.0, 1082.9, 906.5, 1102.7]}, {"text": "25%", "bbox": [996.9, 1082.9, 1029.5, 1102.7]}, {"text": "24%", "bbox": [1119.9, 1082.9, 1152.5, 1102.7]}, {"text": "Expected life (years)", "bbox": [106.2, 1110.0, 254.2, 1129.8]}, {"text": "3", "bbox": [891.2, 1110.0, 900.3, 1129.8]}, {"text": "3", "bbox": [1014.2, 1110.0, 1023.2, 1129.8]}, {"text": "3", "bbox": [1137.2, 1110.0, 1146.2, 1129.8]}, {"text": "Grant-date fair value of underlying Occidental common stock", "bbox": [106.2, 1137.1, 542.1, 1156.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [798.2, 1137.1, 807.2, 1156.9]}, {"text": "69.87", "bbox": [851.4, 1137.1, 892.0, 1156.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [921.1, 1137.1, 930.2, 1156.9]}, {"text": "67.21", "bbox": [974.4, 1137.1, 1015.0, 1156.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1044.1, 1137.1, 1053.1, 1156.9]}, {"text": "76.83", "bbox": [1097.3, 1137.1, 1137.9, 1156.9]}, {"text": "A summary of 